HEADWORD: Stroker
<hw>Strok"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who strokes;
also, one who pretends to cure by stroking.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Cures worked by Greatrix the <qex>stroker</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Bp.
Warburton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Strokesman</ent>⟦br⟧
